# Header

A component for displaying a page header with a logo and navigation items.

## Props

| Prop     | Type   | Default | Description                           |
|----------|--------|---------|---------------------------------------|
| logo     | string |         | The text or image to use for the logo |
| navItems | array  | []      | An array of navigation items to display |

### Navigation Item

| Prop | Type   | Default | Description               |
|------|--------|---------|---------------------------|
| text | string |         | The text of the nav item  |
| href | string |         | The URL of the nav item   |

## Example

```html
<uix-header
  logo="My App"  
  :navItems="[
    { text: 'Home', href: '/' },
    { text: 'About', href: '/about' },
    { text: 'Contact', href: '/contact' }
  ]"
></uix-header>
```